 Have you heard of this woman?

00:09:20.160 --> 00:09:21.000
 - No.

00:09:21.000 --> 00:09:22.880
 - She was basically the most famous woman in the world

00:09:22.880 --> 00:09:25.120
 in the 1920s when tennis was quite the sport

00:09:25.120 --> 00:09:26.280
 and everyone loved it.

00:09:26.280 --> 00:09:27.960
 And she was amazing.

00:09:27.960 --> 00:09:31.120
